Package: levin
Version: 0.0.1
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17), libstdc++6 (>= 9), libcurl4 (>= 7.58), libssl3 | libssl1.1
Maintainer: Levin Contributors <levin@annas-archive.org>
Homepage: https://annas-archive.org
Description: Background torrent seeding client for Anna's Archive
 Levin is a lightweight daemon that downloads and seeds torrents from
 Anna's Archive. It respects device constraints by pausing on battery
 power, managing disk space automatically, and supporting WebTorrent
 for browser-based downloads.
 .
 Features:
  - Automatic torrent fetching from Anna's Archive
  - Disk budget management with configurable limits
  - WebTorrent support for browser peers
  - Systemd user service integration
  - Low resource footprint
